if phone battery icon is = 5 OR <5 percent 
  get a phone charger
if phone charger is found
  plug one end of  phone charger to DC power outlet
if one end of phone charger is connected to DC power outlet
  plug the other end of phone charger to phone
if phone battery icon displays < 100 percent
  continue charging phone 
if phone battery icon displays = 100 percent 
  discontinue phone charging  
if discontinue phone charging  
  unplug phone charger from DC power outlet
  
